{
  "stem": "2590.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But 17,000 Jews, they were evacuated into this [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's what the woods' called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They made them dig graves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And later, they put them in the graves with grenades.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was November, the end of November 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And even nature didn't help because it was raining and snowing and hailing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were dirt roads.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people were walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told the people, even if you didn't declare all your gold and silver or precious things, you can take it with you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whoever-- people carried-- they carried-- they carried food, carried luggage, carried clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a struggle for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some of them escaped, very few, because the Germans had dogs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you escaped, and the dog ran right after you, and they killed you anyway.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after this, we came-- whoever survived survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the ghetto, they didn't touch the people that had the labor cards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I started to work already also, outside cleaning German offices and floors, washing for the Germans, washing their laundry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were already less people in our ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But people from-- and Rowne, it was the first-- they called it actually the first time that they killed-- there was a mass-- mass-- mass killing of so many people at once.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But later on, it happened in all other little villages and cities around Rowne.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the people knew already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So many people escaped and they came to our city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in our city, there was this good German who worked for the mayor from the city, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he helped some Jews he know to get-- more Jews came to the city, and we didn't have ration cards for them, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
